       Name: Momentum Chain
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_IGNORE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 0
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: Your momentum fades.
Acquisition:
   - Crusader: level 5
Description:
   Momentum Chain activates the Crusader's escalating-pressure doctrine,
   granting a damroll bonus that represents each strike building on the
   momentum of the last. The buff reflects the lore's core principle:
   "chain the Knight's body-strikes into the Swordsman's building
   momentum, and the accumulated force exceeds what either path sustains
   alone."

   Costs: Movement (via subtract_energy_cost)
   Cooldown: 20 rounds
   Duration: 5 + (Crusader level / 4) rounds
   Damroll modifier: (Crusader level * 3) + (Knight level * 2)
                     + (Swordsman level * 2)

   Designed to be activated before building a combo sequence, amplifying
   the damage of each war_attack skill used during the chain.
